commit.message:
Confidence Changes

edited confidence levels to be a bit higher to filter out more junk links
removed unused module

Added Sentiment Detection

Added sentiment detection and emotion detection to the transcript.
Also parsed key words from the lecture transcript and generated wikipedia links for further study (resources section)

Python Database Helpers

Added 3 files
1. How to setup (in case we all forget)
2. end_actions.py - used for gathering transcript at the end of the presentation and turning it into a summary (top 40% of the transcript is converted to summary form).
3. speech_to_text.py - uses the mic to translate speech into words. words are uploaded to firebase from where they can be downloaded as a transcript.
fixed first item always showing up
